{"tid":2142741,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★女傭疑為報復幫口罩「加料」 偷口罩塞下體再供僱主用","createTime":"2020-08-06T15:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T21:25:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":339,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"bf626394434c56e6d6aefa62800073ec5a3f6bd2","tid":2142741,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T15:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2715000/2715464/9063a2b2-35de-4110-b404-f0565da4da69_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2715000%2F2715464%2F9063a2b2-35de-4110-b404-f0565da4da69_1024.jpg&h=c2715495&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外傭因對僱主不滿，趁對方不留意暗地裡報復的個案屢見不鮮，最近印尼一名女傭就被發現偷走僱主口罩並塞入褲襠近下體位置，放置一會之後重新掏出並放入口罩盒扮成全新。事主翻看家中閉路電視時發現問題並相關口罩棄掉，又直指女傭是「精神病」呼籲網民留意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2715464/%E3%80%90%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E5%A4%96%E5%82%AD%E3%80%91%E5%A5%B3%E5%82%AD%E7%96%91%E7%82%BA%E5%A0%B1%E5%BE%A9%E5%B9%AB%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E3%80%8C%E5%8A%A0%E6%96%99%E3%80%8D%20%E5%81%B7%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%A1%9E%E4%B8%8B%E9%AB%94%E5%86%8D%E4%BE%9B%E5%83%B1%E4%B8%BB%E7%94%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2715464%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2580%2596%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%2582%25AD%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2582%25AD%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E5%25B9%25AB%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%2596%2599%25E3%2580%258D%2520%25E5%2581%25B7%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E5%25A1%259E%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%2586%258D%25E4%25BE%259B%25E5%2583%25B1%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E7%2594%25A8&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=93152574\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2715464/%E3%80%90%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E5%A4%96%E5%82%AD%E3%80%91%E5%A5%B3%E